data.description: Click the Virtual Tour link to view the 3D walkthrough. Nestled in a serene neighborhood, this 3-bedroom and 2-bathroom residence offers the perfect blend of comfort and style. From the moment you step inside, prepare to be captivated by the open floor plan that seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The kitchen is equipped with sleek black appliances, granite countertops, a generously sized kitchen island, and a convenient breakfast bar. The primary bedroom is located on the main level, complete with an ensuite bathroom and a spacious walk-in closet, providing a tranquil sanctuary. Upstairs, you’ll find two additional bedrooms and a shared bathroom. Step outside to discover a fenced backyard and patio, perfect for creating cherished outdoor memories. The property comes with an attached garage for your convenience, ensuring easy access and secure parking. Don't miss this incredible opportunity to make this house your forever home, schedule a viewing today!
